ronald hovsepian  wikipedia ronald hovsepian from wikipedia the free encyclopedia jump to navigation search ronald w ron hovsepian ronald w ron hovsepian intralinks president chief executive officer and director website httpwwwintralinkscom ronald w ron hovsepian born  is the former president chief executive officer and director of intralinks inc a global provider of secure saas collaboration solutions and virtual data rooms he was previously the president and chief executive officer of novell inc education and careeredit hovsepian received a bachelor of science degree from boston college he started his career at ibm corporation where he held a number of management and executive positions over a year period including worldwide general manager in ibm marketing and services for the distribution industry segment managing product development of hardware and software sales and marketing and services from  to  he worked in venture capital as a managing director with internet capital group he joined novell in  as executive vice president and president worldwide field operations from  to  he was the president and chief executive officer of novell inc hovsepian led the negotiations that resulted in the controversial microsoft and novell deal that was announced in october  in  novell announced that it had agreed to be acquired by attachmate hovsepian left novell on april   after the acquisition of novell by attachmate in early  hovsepian was appointed president chief executive officer and director of intralinks inc  under his leadership intralinks developed intralinks via a secure enterprise file sharing solution and intralinks dealnexus the largest global online deal sourcing network he led intralinks during its acquisitions of pe nexus mergerid and doctrackr he remained at intralinks through its acquisition by synchronoss the leading innovator of cloud solutions secure enterprise productivity and softwarebased activation for companies across the globe in april  hovsepian left synchronoss board serviceedit hovsepian has served as a member of the board of directors for ansys since  and is currently serving as the nonexecutive chairman of the board of directors of ansys since november  he has served as a member of the board of advisors for cloud technology partners a professional services firm in the field of cloud initiatives since august  he also served as a member of the board of directors for ann inc from  – august  in that time he also served as the nonexecutive chairman of the board of directors of ann inc from  –  referencesedit  a b intralinks appoints ronald w hovsepian new ceo december     ppnetnet  the original daily pp and digital media news site » blog archive » microsoft  novell deal ’stinks’ archived from the original on    microsoftnovell deal could create twotier linux market  slashdot linuxslashdotorg retrieved    intralinks releases intralinks via secure file sharing with administrative controls   intralinks launches largest global deal sourcing network  intralinks dealnexus   intralinks launches global deal sourcing network   intralinks acquires mergerid and penexus   dillet romain intralinks acquires document security service doctrackr techcrunch retrieved    synchronoss announces management changes business wire april     httpinvestorsansyscomcorporategovernanceboardofdirectorsaspx board service ansys  httpwwwcloudtpcomannouncementscloudtechnologypartnersnamesronaldhovsepiantoboardofadvisors board service cloud technology partners  httpinvestoranntaylorcomphoenixzhtmlcpirolgovbioid board service ann inc v t e novell systems management edirectory zenworks identity manager access manager bordermanager collaboration open enterprise server groupwise netware people drew major dennis fairclough ray noorda ronald hovsepian eric schmidt other netwars sco v novell star trek project suse linux univel and usl this article about a chief executive from the united states is a stub you can help wikipedia by expanding it v t e retr