lesale he spent more than seventeen years at ibm corporation including three years as worldwide general manager of industry solutions in the retail sector from    with stints in various sales and marketing positions prior to taking profit and loss responsibility at several ibm units he brings a proven track record of achieving revenue goals and profit growth in the it solutions business more recently he was managing an investment team overseeing the top  investments for the internet capital group icg serving on the senior executive team for investments and working directly with many of the companies in which icg invested to help them grow today novell has significantly added to its management team and our ability to deliver business solutions for our customers said messman ron brings broad and deep solutions sales and marketing experience in the technology sector as well as an indepth understanding of the it market and what customers are looking for today having helped customers benefit from solutions before ron can now use those skills to provide novells customers with the secure identity management webbased application development and crossplatform networking solutions they are looking for at ibm hovsepian held various sales marketing and managerial positions including director of consumer driven solutions and vice president global supply chain solutions prior to his role as worldwide general manager of industry solutions following that he served as managing director operations at internet capital group he is currently a member of the board of directors of the ann taylor corporation hovsepian received a bachelor of science degree in marketing from boston college he resides in holliston massachusetts with his wife and their four children about novell novell inc nasdaq novl delivers software for the open enterprise™ with more than  customers in  countries novell helps customers manage simplify secure and integrate their technology environments by leveraging bestofbreed open standardsbased software with over  years of experience more than  employees  partners and support centers around the world novell helps customers gain control over their it operating environment while reducing cost more information about novell can be found at httpwwwnovellcom novell is a registered trademarks nsure extend and nteprise are trademarks and ngage is a service mark of novell inc in the united states and other countries  all thirdparty trademarks are the property of their respective owners the translated version of this page is coming soon in the meantime content will appear in standard north american english  dont show this message again ron hovsepian  wikivisually wikivisually the entire wiki with video and photo galleriesfind something interesting to watch in seconds featured articles  · video picker · language · hover over links in text for more info click links in text for more info ronald hovsepian from wikipedia the free encyclopedia   redirected from ron hovsepian jump to navigation search ronald w ron hovsepian ronald w ron hovsepian intralinks president chief executive officer and director website httpwwwintralinkscom ronald w ron hovsepian born  is the former president chief executive officer and director of intralinks inc a global provider of secure saas collaboration solutions and virtual data rooms he was previously the president and chief executive officer of novell inc education and careeredit hovsepian received a bachelor of science degree from boston college he started his career at ibm corporation where he held a number of management and executive positions over a year period including worldwide general manager in ibm marketing and services for the distribution industry segment managing product development of hardware and software sales and marketing and services from  to  he worked in venture capital as a managing director with internet capital group he joined novell in  as executive vice president and president worldwide field operations from  to  he was the president and chief executive officer of novell inc hovsepian led the negotiations that resulted in the controversial microsoft and novell deal that was announced in october  in  novell announced that it had agreed to be acquired by attachmate hovsepian left novell on april   after the acquisition of novell by attachmate in early  hovsepian was appointed president chief executive officer and director of intralinks inc  under his leadership intralinks developed intralinks via a secure enterprise file sharing solution and intralinks dealnexus the largest global online deal sourcing network he led intralinks during its acquisitions of pe nexus mergerid and doctrackr he remained at intralinks through its acquisition by synchronoss the leading innovator of cloud solutions secure enterprise productivity and softwarebased activation for companies across the globe in april  hovsepian left synchronoss board serviceedit hovsepian has served as a member of the board of directors for ansys since  and is currently serving as the nonexecutive chairman of the board of directors of ansys since november  he has served as a member of the board of advisors for cloud technology partners a professional services firm in the field of cloud initiatives since august  he also served as a member of the board of directors for ann inc from  – august  in that time he also served as the nonexecutive chairman of the board of directors of ann inc from  –  referencesedit  a b intralinks appoints ronald w hovsepian new ceo december     ppnetnet  the original daily pp and digital media news site » blog archive » microsoft  novell deal ’stinks’ archived from the original on    microsoftnovell deal could create twotier linux market  slashdot linuxslashdotorg retrieved    intralinks releases intralinks via secure file sharing with administrative controls   intralinks launches largest global deal sourcing network  intralinks dealnexus   intralinks launches global deal so